# Build-generated reviews snapshot (ADR 0004). The empty default is
# force-committed so typecheck/static imports resolve on a fresh checkout;
# build-time regeneration (real review data) is ignored so it is never
# accidentally staged. Re-commit a deliberate change with `git add -f`.
src/data/reviews.snapshot.json

